[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "これも返されるんだろうな、えいっ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_00464",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "もっと必死にやったほうがいいぞ、シトリン",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_00465",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "これまでの攻撃方法、すべてに対応……\n隙がない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_037_00466",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "生憎ともうとっくにネタ切れでね……\nしかも、真綿で絞め殺すみたいにじわじわと……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_00467",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "長兄の威厳を示す雄大さと形容してほしいが。\nそれともゼロのようにやってほしいか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_00468",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "ほれほれ、どうした？　一瞬でも休めば\n地面と接吻じゃぞ？　接吻の意味が分かるか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_00469",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "も、もうダメだよ、こんなの……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_00470",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "泣き言は粋じゃないよ！\n今は耐えるんだ、ゼロ姉の体力だって無限じゃない！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_00471",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "その通りじゃな。ま、うぬらが力尽きるほうが\n早いじゃろうがの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_00472",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "諦めるんだな。\n兄や姉にはかなわない、そういうものだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_00473",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "そんな風に思い上がっていられるのも、今だけよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00474",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ヘルト、ゼロ……あんたたちの厄介な\n手駒はもういない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00475",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "ふん、それがどうした。そいつを倒したところで\nそいつが石化させたモノが治るわけでもない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_00476",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "そうね。石化を治すのは、\n頼りになる私の仲間たちよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00477",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "フン……その錬金術士の筆頭たるレスナも\n石になっているであろうが",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_00478",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "アルビーナも、他のみんなもいる……\n治してくれるはず！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00479",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "それにレスナとて、果たしてそこまで労して\n治す価値のある人物かどうか……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_00480",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "せっかく、色々と試練を考えていたのに\n最初の試練であっさりと脱落してしまった期待外れだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_00481",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "この期に及んで、試練ですって？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00482",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "我らは人類を「管理」する上位存在として、\nレスナを試しているのじゃ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_00483",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "レスナが人類を導く器たる人間かどうか、\n精神を試す問題を用意していたのさ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_00484",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "思い上がりも甚だしいったらないね、そいつぁ……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_00485",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "たとえば、うぬらの縁者のフロッケなる少女。\nあの子は良い子じゃの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_00486",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ちょ、ちょっと……！\nあんたたち、あの子に何かするつもり！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00487",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "兄の話は最後まで聞け。そういうところだぞ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_00488",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "彼女は他者を気遣う心を持ち、争いを好まない。\n実に素晴らしい、「管理」されるべき人類の模範だ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_00489",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "だが、調べてみると彼女の両親はまだ\n娘を使った金儲けを画策しているじゃないか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_00490",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "それは……だから、私たちはもうフロッケが両親に\n会わないようにって引き離して……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00491",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "それは何も問題を解決しておらぬ。\n先送りにしただけであろう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_00492",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "よって試練の１つとして、フロッケを両親と再び\n引き合わせて、レスナがそれをどう処理するか見たい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_00493",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "そんなの、絶対ロクなことにならない……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00494",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "調べた限りフロッケの両親は\nランターナ王国の法に触れたかは非常に曖昧だ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_00495",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "法では裁けぬ悪にどう対処するのか、それによって\nレスナの器も分かるというものじゃろう？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_00496",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "そんな、人の家庭を、人生を勝手に試練にして……！\nそれでフロッケが酷い目にあったらどうするの！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00497",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "度合いによっては我々が「管理」することになるが。\nそれは知ったことではない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_00498",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "ね？　ロクでもないでしょ？\nだーーーからヘルトとゼロの相手は嫌だったんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_00499",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "うん、よーーーっく、分かった。\nこいつらを野放しにしちゃいけないってね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00500",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "まだまだ！　徹底抗戦よ！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00501",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]